    },
    {
      "id": "9a437d4f_d047684a",
      "file_path": "PolicyEngineClient/pom.xml",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 49,
      "message": "I see, thanks Tarun.  I think best to leave in test directory if no usage (or remove).   If it is not marked as JUnit @Test annotation (or @Ignore if they are marked as such) I believe sonar won't take into account for coverage metrics, and test won't be run.  Unless you found out otherwise.   In any case, if the code is for sample purposes, better to have it in test, or remove.",
      "author": {
